Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=========Pre=========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=========OP=========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.22,0:00:05.73,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}悲しみ連鎖の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.92,0:00:15.37,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}僕らの願いが届くまで…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.59,0:00:24.26,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}大事なものまた一つ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:28.88,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}モノクロの空へと消える
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:35.67,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}隠したキズ冷たく震え
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.11,0:00:40.05,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}自分の居場所を探す
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.41,0:00:47.86,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}常識に従うこの世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:52.58,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}どうしようもできないことを
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.43,0:00:56.78,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}壊していきたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.85,0:01:04.33,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}閉ざしたココロ叫んでいる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.22,0:01:11.78,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}悲しみ連鎖の中で僕らは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.88,0:01:17.42,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}自分さえも見失いそうになって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.10,0:01:21.35,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}曖昧な答えはイラナイ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.45,0:01:27.86,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}確かな今　追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.22,0:00:05.73,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在悲伤的连锁之中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.92,0:00:15.37,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在我们的愿望实现之前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.59,0:00:24.26,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}又一件珍贵的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:28.88,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}消失在黑白的空中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:35.67,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}隐藏的伤痕在发冷颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.11,0:00:40.05,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}去找寻我的容身之处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.41,0:00:47.86,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在这个遵循常识的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:52.58,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}想打破无可救药的桎梏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.43,0:00:56.78,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}按自己的意志自由生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.85,0:01:04.33,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}封闭的心灵正发出呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.22,0:01:11.78,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在悲伤的连锁之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.88,0:01:17.42,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我们几乎快要迷失自我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.10,0:01:21.35,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}不需要暧昧的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.45,0:01:27.86,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}只需去追寻真切的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======TEXT=======
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.14,0:01:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时刻不能放松戒备
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.16,0:01:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全军准备出动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.17,0:01:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.02,0:01:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从范乌哲失陷后战况不容乐观
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.34,0:01:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格雷戈尔将军如此不堪一击…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.45,0:01:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 但考虑到对手是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.39,0:01:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非完全无法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.25,0:01:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔金·巩特尔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.82,0:01:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战线正压向我方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.27,0:02:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更糟糕的是 失去范乌哲后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.87,0:02:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经失去了打持久战的资本
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.96,0:02:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是时候也该有大动作了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.75,0:02:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着你提醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下场战役的部署即将完成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.95,0:02:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必杞人忧天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候不容你不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.07,0:02:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在待命便是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么对我也保密吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…耶格尔将军
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.86,0:02:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问件事可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.91,0:02:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是什么关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.69,0:02:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么问这个…你莫非
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.42,0:02:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.74,0:02:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详情我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.78,0:02:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他们的关系远比看上去复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛尔贝莉亚 我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.98,0:03:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时也是这种蓝色玫瑰的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您让我找到了自己的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没有这样一起赏花了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.79,0:04:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人回想起过去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能站在这缕阳光下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能伴随殿下身边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.41,0:04:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都源自于您的慈悲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从那时 您为我斩断枷锁以来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.02,0:04:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的未来 只为您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.21,0:05:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 为什么我会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 一个个六神无主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.06,0:05:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 队长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.79,0:05:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉鲁高
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.86,0:05:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你确认没事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.13,0:05:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要的话可以找我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:05:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 不过我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.66,0:06:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉让你操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有会议 我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.69,0:06:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.42,0:06:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说自己没事的人 往往都心事重重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.57,0:07:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里着火了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.43,0:07:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.59,0:07:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.62,0:07:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想…烤点面包
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一副问题堆积如山的表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.24,0:07:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.49,0:07:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 还好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 别心不在焉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.58,0:07:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候害艾丽西娅受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功夺取范乌哲后 战争主动权正倒向我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝国军失去资源供应保障后 势必策划短期决战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.74,0:07:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须密切关注帝国军动向 谨慎应对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.81,0:07:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.69,0:07:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔金 我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巩特尔少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切忌松懈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉鲁高 有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.41,0:08:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事的人是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给个面子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.62,0:08:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是块掏心置腹的好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帐篷…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.86,0:08:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿 进去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.73,0:08:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.23,0:09:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正所谓坦诚相见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“火箭筒中一株萝卜花”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.97,0:09:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“姑娘用笑颜将它栽培”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.44,0:09:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“心中深藏的…”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队里竟然还准备了这种设施
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有建树的部队 待遇果然不同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,补给方面也好说话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗 我们两个人独占
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.08,0:09:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么大不了的 洗第一缸水而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和我谈什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说的来着 人生在世不如意者十之八九
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.05,0:09:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身经百战的队长 在那方面还是新兵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.94,0:09:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看都看得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:09:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们进展不顺利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 你们是指谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们并不是那种…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.51,0:10:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我只要第七小队运转顺畅就满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.23,0:10:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我给你讲个故事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.40,0:10:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次大战中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.91,0:10:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个新兵 刚入伍时连东南西北都分不清
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只因为想保卫国家 所以拿起枪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加入了义勇军
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时一心就是打仗杀敌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这个一无所有的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.98,0:10:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过战场上的历练 终于也有了自己的好友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.09,0:11:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至还有了喜欢的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉鲁高
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来介绍 这位是我的好友拉鲁高
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是今天开始加入义勇军的埃莉诺·帕罗特上等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.87,0:11:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.73,0:11:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.59,0:11:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个从未谈过恋爱的大老爷们儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,略显笨拙的 也开始努力尝试
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.28,0:11:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手法是笨到家了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.98,0:11:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知该如何赢得那位姑娘的芳心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕比上战场还辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.67,0:11:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只因为今天和姑娘说过话了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天姑娘主动向自己打招呼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就乐不可支
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后嘛 就是约定俗成的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.22,0:12:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方也没有太为难他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.65,0:12:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦诚心意了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.70,0:12:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.43,0:12:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚想说出口时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.91,0:12:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就从姑娘嘴里得知自己的好友也喜欢她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家潇洒 又有男人味
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.38,0:12:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个值得依靠的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战场上也好几次救过自己
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考虑到为了姑娘 他们也更般配
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.79,0:12:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内心当然挣扎过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.99,0:12:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是友情 还是自己的爱情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.58,0:12:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是能够轻易说服自己的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.25,0:12:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是得出结论前 他的那位好友就战死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.63,0:12:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过从结果看 他最后选择了友情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:13:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时一下子发生了太多事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位姑娘没有察觉到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.59,0:13:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算伤心 也没必要让大家都不幸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家明知才会这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃莉诺才没那么笨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃莉诺就是那位帕罗特上尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 不许告诉任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说出去要你好看！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.94,0:13:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（没打算说出去 全都是你在自曝…）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.97,0:13:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.21,0:13:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.03,0:13:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这样的人生不适合队长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.19,0:13:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢谢 拉鲁高
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.92,0:13:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以 请收好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.07,0:14:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.30,0:14:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…你不是要外出吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.73,0:14:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样 也没有麻烦你送我的必然性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.49,0:14:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.66,0:14:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.65,0:14:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开个玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能麻烦送我去集市吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.09,0:14:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.58,0:14:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必然性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.00,0:14:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没有必然性 这样能省力些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样…那走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 请多关照 拉玛尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你用名字称呼我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.97,0:14:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是心理作用 快开车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.46,0:14:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢今天陪我来购物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…反正闲着慌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.12,0:15:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.16,0:15:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 今天真是大采购啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是买给谁的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近 哥哥看起来有点消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.75,0:15:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想给他做点好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.29,0:15:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真懂事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.19,0:16:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.95,0:16:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥是我唯一的亲人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.21,0:16:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能总是为别人操心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.10,0:16:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次的事也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.92,0:16:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事 习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.87,0:16:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真坚强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.65,0:16:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻木了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.42,0:16:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算不上什么坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果有朝一日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都能对错的事说不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为那样的世界就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.06,0:16:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.10,0:16:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔迪奥是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.12,0:17:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 整天恍恍惚惚的不像我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须搞个明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔金
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.26,0:17:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.89,0:17:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事想找你谈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.44,0:17:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们最近不太搭调
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉尴尬…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:17:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.76,0:18:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我也感觉不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的顶头上司
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.25,0:18:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后总还要并肩作战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.41,0:18:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 让你有这种顾虑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.92,0:18:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要的不是道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.35,0:18:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想 像以前那样聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.03,0:18:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔金呢 怎么想？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.27,0:18:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.43,0:18:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想继续这样尴尬下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为自己被维尔金讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.38,0:18:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要讨厌…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.82,0:18:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说什么讨厌 我其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.07,0:18:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是重要的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.96,0:19:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的…伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 和好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样法尔迪奥也会安心的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.95,0:19:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要提法尔迪奥？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他好像很担心…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.72,0:19:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我和维尔金的问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.71,0:19:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和法尔迪奥有关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.99,0:19:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔迪奥向我告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.31,0:19:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.98,0:19:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…法尔迪奥是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是问这些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在问维尔金的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问我这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.40,0:19:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.60,0:20:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是艾丽西娅和法尔迪奥的问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没资格插嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.74,0:20:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的这么想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.61,0:20:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你心甘情愿这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.41,0:20:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.47,0:21:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来啦 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.19,0:21:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没做了 有点失败
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.48,0:21:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======ED=======
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:47.31,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}悲しすぎる瞳が
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.77,0:21:53.98,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}この空を映す
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.35,0:22:02.37,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}掛ける言葉がわからずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.65,0:22:08.22,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}ただ　星を数えた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.74,0:22:13.94,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}孤独で居る世界は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.32,0:22:20.72,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}得意なはずだと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.04,0:22:27.23,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}振りかえる日々　あぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.68,0:22:33.66,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}探していた　きみをひとり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.87,0:22:40.30,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}もしもいま許されるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:46.99,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}きみのことだけ想うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.15,0:22:54.88,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}忘れたくない悲しみならば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.34,0:23:02.42,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}ただそれが　それだけが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.76,0:23:08.62,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)\be1}そう  ひとつの願い
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:47.31,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}太过悲伤的眼眸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.77,0:21:53.98,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}映照出这片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.35,0:22:02.37,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}不知该说什么好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.65,0:22:08.22,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}只默默数着星星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.74,0:22:13.94,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}孤独的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.32,0:22:20.72,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}早该习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.04,0:22:27.23,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}回首往日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.68,0:22:33.66,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}我曾独自将你找寻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.87,0:22:40.30,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}若此刻能得到允许
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:46.99,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}我愿心中只思念着你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.15,0:22:54.88,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}若不愿忘却这悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.34,0:23:02.42,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}仅此而已 唯有此心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.76,0:23:08.62,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)\be1}是的 那是唯一的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======NEXT=======
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.14,0:23:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫伊莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.88,0:23:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全名就是伊莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.62,0:23:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达鲁库斯人自古没有姓氏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.96,0:23:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我被巩特尔家收为养女后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.93,0:23:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一种不可思议的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.23,0:23:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥说 这就是一家人的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.59,0:23:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 战场女武神
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.94,0:23:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第17章 精灵节的馈赠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.81,0:23:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿命的意义 在于与其抗争 而非屈服
